Package: padr
Type: Package
Title: Quickly get time series data ready for analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Edwin Thoen
Maintainer: Edwin Thoen <edwinthoen@gmail.com>
Description: The padr package helps transforming raw time series data to a format ready for analysis. It offers two functionalities; aggregating data to a higher level interval (thicken) and filling in records where observations were absent (pad). It offers a few functions that assist at filling missing values after padding.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports:
    dplyr,
    Rcpp
Suggests:
    testthat,
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    tidyr
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
LinkingTo: Rcpp
VignetteBuilder: knitr
